      "span_text": "ELISA We assayed the concentration of cardiac 4-HNE in TO-2 hamsters using OxiSelect HNE-His Adduct ELISA Kit (Cell Biolabs, Inc, San Diego, CA, USA) according to the protocol supplied with the kit.  In brief, 100 μl of the 10 μg/ml protein samples from whole hearts of TO-2 hamsters were probed with an anti-4-HNE antibody and absorbed on a microplate reader using 450 nm as the primary wavelength."
